"url=\"http://www.siemens.com\">Heinrich Ruthensteiner</ulink> of Siemens, "
"<ulink url=\"http://schwer.us\">Augie Schwer</ulink>, <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.wikipedia.org\">Mark Bergsma</ulink>, <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.forfun.net\">Marco Davids</ulink>, <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.opensuse.org\">Marcus Rueckert of OpenSUSE</ulink>, Andre "
"Muraro of <ulink url=\"http://www.locaweb.com.br\">Locaweb</ulink>, Antony "
"Lesuisse, <ulink url=\"http://www.linuxnetworks.de\">Norbert "
"Sendetzky</ulink>, <ulink url=\"http://www.aruba.it\">Marco "
