msgid ""
"Thanks to <ulink url=\"http://www.easydns.com\">EasyDNS</ulink>, PowerDNS "
"now supports multiple masters per domain. For configuration details, see "
"<xref linkend=\"slave\"/>. Implemented in c1018, c1017."
