#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:3252
msgid ""
"Thanks to <ulink url=\"http://www.easydns.com\">EasyDNS</ulink>, PowerDNS "
"now supports the KEY record type, as well the SPF record. In c976."
