#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:3257
msgid ""
"Added support for CERT, SSHFP, DNSKEY, DS, NSEC, RRSIG record types, as part "
"of the move to the new DNS parsing/generating code."
