#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:4403
msgid ""
"Currently several big ISPs are evaluating the PowerDNS recursor for their "
"resolving needs, some of them have switched already.  In the course of "
"testing, over 350 million actual queries have been recorded and replayed, "
"the answers turn out to be satisfactorily."
