#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:5582
msgid ""
"Silly 'wuh' debugging output in zone2sql and bindbackend removed (spotted by "
"Ivo van der Wijk)."
