"Sadly, due to <ulink "
"url=\"http://sources.redhat.com/ml/libc-alpha/2003-01/msg00245.html\">technical "
"reasons</ulink>, compiling the pdns recursor and pdns authoritative "
"nameserver into one binary is not immediately possible. During the release "
