#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:6419
msgid ""
"pipe backend gains the ability to restricts its invocation to a limited "
"number of requests. This allows a very busy nameserver to still serve "
"packets from a slow perl backend."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:6425
msgid ""
