"index. If you've previously copy pasted the commands and not noticed the "
"error, execute <command>CREATE INDEX rec_name_index ON "
"records(name)</command> to remedy. Thanks to Jeff Miller for reporting "
"this. This also lead to depressingly slow 'ANY' lookups for those of you "
"doing benchmarks."
