#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:7479
msgid ""
"PostgreSQL users should be aware that while 1.99.10 works with the schema as "
"presented in earlier versions, advanced features such as master or slave "
"support will not work unless you create the new 'domains' table as well."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:7487
msgid ""
"Wildcard AAAA queries sometimes received an NXDOMAIN error where they should "
"have gotten an empty NO ERROR. Thanks to Jeroen Massar for spotting this on "
"the .TK TLD!"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:7493
msgid ""
"Do not disable the packetcache for 'recursion desired' packets unless a "
"recursor was configured. Thanks to Greg Schueler for noticing this."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:7498
msgid ""
"A failing backend would not be reinstated. Thanks to 'Webspider' for "
"discovering this problem with PostgreSQL connections that die after "
"prolonged inactivity."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:7504
msgid ""
"Fixed loads of IPv6 transport problems. Thanks to Marco Davids and others "
"for testing. Considered ready for production now."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:7510
msgid ""
"<command>Zone2sql</command> printed a debugging statement on range $GENERATE "
"commands. Thanks to Rene van Valkenburg for spotting this."
