#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:7520
msgid ""
"PDNS can now act as a master, sending out notifications in case of changes "
"and allowing slaves to AXFR. Big rewording of replication support, domains "
"are now either 'native', 'master' or 'slave'. See <xref "
"linkend=\"replication\"/> for lots of details."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:7526
