"<command>Zone2sql</command> in PostgreSQL mode now populates the 'domains' "
"table for easy master, slave or native replication support."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:7531
msgid ""
"Ability to disable those annoying Windows DNS Dynamic Update messages from "
"appearing in the log. See <function>log-failed-updates</function> in <xref "
"linkend=\"all-settings\"/>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:7537
msgid "Ability to run on IPv6 transport only"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:7542
msgid ""
"Logging can now happen under a 'facility' so all PDNS messages appear in "
"their own file. See <xref linkend=\"syslog\"/>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
