#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><para><warning><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:12800
msgid ""
"This section is aimed at programmers wanting to contribute to the recursor, "
"or to help fix bugs. It is not required reading for a PowerDNS operator, "
"although it might prove interesting."
