#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: docs/pdns.xml:14790
msgid "LOG"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:14793
msgid ""
"For specifying things that should be logged. Can only be sent after a query "
"and before an END line. After the tab, the message to be logged."
