#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para><screen>
#: docs/pdns.xml:14809
#, no-wrap
msgid "DATA\tqname\t\tqclass\tqtype\tttl\tid\tcontent\t\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:14763
msgid ""
"Each answer starts with a tag, possibly followed by a TAB and more data.  "
"<placeholder type=\"variablelist\" id=\"0\"/> So, letting it be known that "
"there is no data consists of sending 'END' without anything else.  The "
"answer format (for abi-version 1 and 2): <placeholder type=\"screen\" "
"id=\"1\"/> 'content' is as specified in <xref linkend=\"types\"/>. For MX "
"and SRV, content consists of the priority, followed by a tab, followed by "
"the actual content."
msgstr ""

