#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18479
msgid ""
"PowerDNS uses pthreads too, and to ease the porting process we decided not "
"to reinvent the wheel, but to use pthreads for Windows instead."
