#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18487
msgid ""
"Pthreads for Windows is available from anonymous ftp at <ulink "
"url=\"ftp://sources.redhat.com/pub/pthreads-win32/\">ftp://sources.redhat.com/pub/pthreads-win32/</ulink>.  "
"You should download the latest <filename>pthreads-YYYY-MM-DD.exe</filename> "
"file."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><note><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18493
msgid ""
"PowerDNS for Windows was tested with the snapshot of 2002-03-02 of the "
"library."
