#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18498
msgid ""
"For more information you can visit the pthreads for Windows homepage at "
"<ulink "
"url=\"http://sources.redhat.com/pthreads-win32/\">http://sources.redhat.com/pthreads-win32/</ulink>"
