#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><title>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18503
msgid "Installing pthreads for Windows"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18506
msgid ""
"To install the pthreads for Windows library you have to locate your "
"<filename>pthreads-YYYY-MM-DD.exe</filename> file and start it."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18511
msgid ""
"After starting the executable a self-extractor dialog will show up where you "
"can specify where to extract the contents of the file. When you selected a "
"location you can press the <guibutton>Extract</guibutton> button to extract "
"all content to the target directory."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18517
msgid ""
"The library is now installed, we still have to tell Visual C++ where it's "
"located though, more on that later."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><title>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18526
msgid "Nullsoft Installer"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18529
msgid ""
"For our installation program we used Nullsoft's Installer System "
"(<acronym>NSIS</acronym>). We used <acronym>NSIS</acronym> because it's easy "
"to use, versatile and free (and it uses "
"<acronym><trademark>SuperPiMP</trademark></acronym> technology, but they "
"refuse to tell us what it is ;)). If the name Nullsoft rings a bell, it's "
"because they're the guys who made <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.winamp.com/\">winamp</ulink>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><title>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18536
msgid "Getting the Nullsoft Installer"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18539
msgid ""
"The Nullsoft Installer can be downloaded at their website, which is located "
"at <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.nullsoft.com/free/nsis/\">http://www.nullsoft.com/free/nsis/</ulink>.  "
"The file that you should download is called <filename>nsisXXX.exe</filename> "
"(where XXX is the latest version)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><note><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18546
msgid "You can find the <acronym>NSIS</acronym> documentation at that website too."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><title>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18552
msgid "Installing the Nullsoft Installer"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18555
msgid ""
"Installing <acronym>NSIS</acronym> is easy. All there is to it is locating "
"the installer and execute it.  Then just follow the installation steps."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><title>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18563
msgid "Setting up the build-environment"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18566
msgid ""
"Before starting Microsoft Visual C++ and compile PowerDNS for Windows, you "
"first have to set up your build environment."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><title>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18571
msgid ""
"Make Microsoft Visual C++ recognize <filename>*.cc</filename> and "
"<filename>*.hh</filename> (optional)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18574
msgid ""
"All PowerDNS source files are in the form <filename>name.cc</filename>, and "
"all header files in the form <filename>name.hh</filename>. These extensions "
"aren't recognized by <acronym>MSVC</acronym> by default, so you might want "
"to change that first."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><note><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18581
msgid ""
"Only perform this step if you want to be able to edit the "
"<filename>*.cc</filename> and <filename>*.hh</filename> files in "
"<acronym>MSVC</acronym>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><caution><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18588
msgid ""
"If you decide to perform this step, remember that it requires modification "
"of the Windows registry, always make a backup before modifying!"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18594
msgid ""
"Ok, after that word of caution we can now proceed. You have to follow these "
"steps:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18601
msgid ""
"Start the registry editor by entering <filename>regedit.exe</filename> in "
"the run prompt (<guimenu>Start-&gt;Run...</guimenu>)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18608
msgid ""
"Right click on <filename>HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT</filename> and select "
"<guimenu>New-&gt;Key</guimenu>.  A new key will appear, change that key to "
"<quote><filename>.cc</filename></quote>, then change the default value to "
"<quote>cppfile</quote>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18614
msgid ""
"Then perform the same step for <quote><filename>.hh</filename></quote> (use "
"<quote>hfile</quote> instead of <quote>cppfile</quote>)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18620
msgid ""
"Go to "
"<filename>HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Software\\Microsoft\\DevStudio\\6.0\\Build "
"System\\Components\\Platforms\\Win32 (x86)\\Tools\\32-bit C/C++ Compiler for "
"80x86</filename>. And add <quote>;*.cc</quote> to the "
"<filename>Input_Spec</filename> value (so that it becomes "
"<quote>*.c;*.cpp;*.cxx;*.cc</quote>)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><orderedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18626
msgid ""
"If you happen to use another platform (like alpha) to compile the sources, "
"you have to do the step above for that platform."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18633
msgid ""
"Go to "
"<filename>HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Software\\Microsoft\\DevStudio\\6.0\\Search</filename>. "
"And add <quote>;*.cc;*.hh</quote> to the <filename>FIF_Filter</filename> "
"value (so that it becomes "
"<quote>*.c;*.cpp;*.cxx;*.tli;*.h;*.tlh;*.inl;*.rc;*.cc;*.hh</quote>)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18640
msgid ""
"Finally change "
"<filename>HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Software\\Microsoft\\DevStudio\\6.0\\Text "
"Editor\\Tabs/Language Settings\\C/C++</filename>. And add "
"<quote>;cc;hh</quote> to the <filename>FileExtensions</filename> value (so "
"that it becomes "
"<quote>cpp;cxx;c;h;hxx;hpp;inl;tlh;tli;rc;rc2;hh;cc</quote>)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18647
msgid "Close the registry editor."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18654
msgid ""
"Now should <acronym>MSVC</acronym> properly recognize the files as being "
"C++."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><title>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18660
msgid "Setting Microsoft Visual C++'s directories"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18663
msgid ""
"<acronym>MSVC</acronym> needs to locate some include files, libraries and "
"executables when it has to build PowerDNS for Windows. We are now going to "
"tell <acronym>MSVC</acronym> where to find those."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18669
msgid ""
"To enter the directory dialog you have to go to "
"<guimenu>Tools-&gt;Options...-&gt;Directories</guimenu>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><title>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18673
msgid "Setting the pthreads directories"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18676
msgid ""
"When you are in the directory dialog you can add the pthreads for Windows "
"directory."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18680
msgid ""
"First add the include directory, to do this you have to select "
"<guilabel>Include files</guilabel> from the <guilabel>Show directories "
"for:</guilabel> combobox. Then press the <guibutton>New</guibutton> button "
"and browse to the <command>include</command> directory of pthreads "
"(ie. <filename>C:\\pthreads\\include</filename>)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18686
msgid ""
"Then switch to <guilabel>Library files</guilabel> and add the "
"<command>library</command> directory "
"(ie. <filename>C:\\pthreads\\lib</filename>) using the same method as above."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><title>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18692
msgid "Setting the Nullsoft Installer directory"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><sect4><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18695
msgid ""
"While still being in the directory dialog, switch to <guilabel>Executable "
"files</guilabel> and add the Nullsoft Installer directory "
"(ie. <filename>C:\\Program Files\\NSIS</filename>) to the list."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><title>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18705
msgid "Compilation"
