#. type: Content of: <book><appendix><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: docs/pdns.xml:18716
msgid ""
"To start the compilation you first have to open the PowerDNS workspace "
"(<filename>powerdns.dsw</filename>) using explorer or from the "
"<guimenu>File-&gt;Open Workspace...</guimenu> menu in "
"<acronym>MSVC</acronym>."
